==Powers and Abilities==
===Powers===
{{Quote|Enjoy the now, baby. It's the only thing that's certain.|Lilia Calderu to [[William Kaplan]]|Familiar by Thy Side}}
*'''[[Magic]]''': Lilia was born a witch, allowing her to tap into the mystical forces of the universe and manipulate the world around her. Her specialty is divination, the art of seeing future events and gaining information through magical means.
**'''[[Magic#Witchcraft|Witchcraft]]''': Having been alive for centuries, Calderu is a powerful and experienced witch. Her magic manifests in the color of yellow. Although she stopped using due to wanting to end her "gaps," Calderu was an extremely powerful and experienced witch.
***'''Magical Energy Manipulation''': Calderu was able to make her fist glow yellow when [[Agatha Harkness]] started insulting her and the rest of her [[Agatha Harkness' Coven|coven]] in a attempt to steal their power.
***'''Spell Casting''': Aside from her gifts in divination, Calderu, like every witch, has the ability to cast spells. This is done through certain hand gestures and incantations spoken in Latin. She performed a ritual to create a broomstick, giving it the ability to fly. Calderu is also able to put a powerful protective sigil on people to keep their identity safe from others. She did this to [[William Kaplan]] at his Bar Mitzvah after reading his fortune, concealing his identity to witchfolk.
****'''Gravity Manipulation''': Calderu used a tarot card spell to invert gravity, flipping {{WPS|The Tower (tarot card)|The Tower}} card upright and plunging the [[Salem Seven]] into the numerous blades hanging from the room's ceiling.
***'''[[Magic#Divination|Divination]]''': Calderu is a witch who specialized in employing divination, a method of reading the future, the present, and the past to provide help to a problem at hand. Divination relies on a range of occult or ritual means, including tarot cards, crystal balls, and palm reading.
****'''Precognition''': [[File:Agatha All Along Teaser Trailer (100).png|thumb|250px|Calderu receives a precognition of the [[Spirit Witch Trial]]]] Calderu's magic typically manifests as the ability to predict the future. Divination appears to be triggered involuntarily, and its manifestations can range from visions and flashes that cause her significant pain, which may or may not cause her to perform involuntary gestures and movements, to small insights popping into her mind out of nowhere, such as Calderu looking at a person and mentioning the name of a tarot card. While reading [[Wiccan|Billy Kaplan]]'s fortune at his Bar Mitzvah, Calderu had a divination about [[Billy Maximoff]] reincarnating into his body after his death. Calderu received a precognition of the [[Spirit Witch Trial]], in which she partook in the future, when she was being [[Search for Coven Members#Lilia Calderu|recruited]] into Harkness' coven.
****'''Clairvoyance''': Calderu's magic allows her acquire information using sight outside the normal range of detection about an object, person, location, or physical event. Calderu was able to see the [[Salem Seven]] entering the [[Witches' Road]] in her dream.
****'''[[Time Travel|Chronoskimming]]''': Calderu's magic allows her to send her consciousness to past or future versions of herself. She referred to this as "gaps". During her [[Divination Witch Trial|trial]], Calderu involuntarily sent her consciousness into the past and future, leading to out-of-context sentences being spoken at different points in time, making her unable to properly communicate her divinations.
***'''Longevity''': Lilia lived for over 450 years. She explained that, during her prime, she was constantly chased out of every village she passed through after accurately predicting tragedy.

===Abilities===
*'''Musician:''' Calderu studied the zils and pan flute. She also plays the triangle, maracas, and tambourine.
*'''Bilingualism''': Calderu is fluent in her native Sicilian and English.

