==Trivia==
*In the comics, Lilia Calderu is the leader of a coven tasked with keeping the [[Book of Cagliostro]], being a descendant of [[Cagliostro]] himself. She was also a descendant of the first Baron Mordo, and became romantically involved with her half-uncle [[Karl Mordo]]. She fell in love with him and bore a daughter, Astrid, but he only pretended to be in love to steal the Book from her.
*Calderu's outfit features many symbols, including an eye, symbolizing herself looking ahead and behind. It also has a drawing of herself looking into the sunset and a drawing of witches passing knowledge onto each other.{{Ref|TMoAAA}}

==Behind the Scenes==
*[[Patti LuPone]] broke her wrist during filming ''[[Agatha All Along]]'', forcing her to hide her wrist from the camera while playing Calderu for one episode.<ref>[https://www.tiktok.com/@marvel/video/7431744783741160735 Marvel Entertainment on TikTok - October 30, 2024]</ref>
*The dynamic between Calderu and [[Death]] was created by actors [[Patti LuPone]] and [[Aubrey Plaza]] organically during filming.{{Ref|TMoAAA}}
*[[Nikki Stanley]] and [[Shannon Murray]] were stunt doubles for [[Patti LuPone]] in the role of Lilia Calderu.

